scripts.deps: npm install && go get && go get -u github.com/variadico/scaneo
scripts.writeSchema: go run main.go --schema && npm run scan
scripts.createConfig: go run main.go --listUp && go run main.go --createConfig
scripts.preprocess: go run main.go --preprocess && npm run writeSchema
scripts.allPreprocess: npm run createConfig && npm run preprocess
scripts.kml: go run main.go --insertSP && go run main.go --convertToJSON && python cmd/exportSPtoKML.py
scripts.csv: go run main.go --insertSP && go run main.go --convertToCSV
scripts.setupDB: go run main.go --migrate && go run main.go --insert
